---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — Emmanuel Akanmu" dim={true}>
  <article class="wrap page">
    <p class="eyebrow">about</p>
    <h1>The origin story</h1>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        Software engineer at Walmart Global Tech. I build AI systems — agents, MCP
        tooling, LLM-integrated infrastructure — that run in production and solve real
        problems for real users.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm actively looking for my next role: frontier AI lab, Forward Deployed
        Engineer, or applied AI engineering. Somewhere the problem is hard, the
        feedback is live, and the work is consequential.
      </p>
      <p>
        My conviction: LLMs are one transition. The next one is embodied. AI that
        moves, perceives, and acts in the physical world is not a decade away — the
        stack is converging faster than the mainstream believes, and the leverage
        point isn't the hardware. It's the software and product layer on top of it.
        That's where I want to be, and what I'm building toward.
      </p>
      <p>
        I believe intelligence is the highest-leverage asset a person can hold —
        applied, compounding, stacked deliberately over time. My goal is to use mine
        to build systems that matter and a life I designed on purpose.
      </p>

      <p class="resume-cta">
        <a class="resume-link" href="/emmanuel-akanmu-resume.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          View résumé (PDF) →
        </a>
      </p>

      <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/fallennyx">GitHub</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/emmanuelakanmu/">LinkedIn</a></li>
        <li><a href="/emmanuel-akanmu-resume.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Résumé</a></li>
        <li><a href="mailto:1eakanmu@gmail.com">Email</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .page { padding-top: 3rem; }
  .page h1 { font-size: clamp(34px, 7vw, 52px); color: #fff; margin: 14px 0 2rem; }
  .resume-cta { margin: 1.75rem 0 0; }
  .resume-link {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: background 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .resume-link:hover {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #000;
  }
</style>
